title: Couple With Heart Person Person Medium Dark Skin Tone
alsoKnownAs: Couple with Heart (Person, Man, Medium-Dark Skin Tone)
description: Represents a romantic couple where the person has a medium-dark skin tone and the man has a medium-dark skin tone, with a heart between them symbolizing love and affection.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, this loving couple emoji is rendered with tender care, showcasing two figures embracing.  The woman-person, depicted with a medium-dark skin tone, is central, with a heart emoji appearing between them, glowing with Apple’s characteristic soft gradients and subtle shine.  The overall impression is one of deep affection and partnership, with smooth, rounded forms that emphasize connection and togetherness in digital conversations.
